posting_body: ['Enjoy our Sparkling Pool!', 'Where Luxury Meets Comfort', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 7', 'OR Text', '7', 'to', 'show contact info', 'for more information.', 'Park Kiely Apartments', '355 Kiely Blvd., San Jose, CA, 95129', 'See our property details here:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 763 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Upscale, Expansive Living at Park Kiely', "When you live at the apartments of Park Kiely, you'll truly have it all.", 'Newly upgraded studio, one and two bedroom residences, filled with features and finishes to make every day brighter.', 'An incredible abundance of amenities, from sports and fitness to relaxation and business.', "Best of all, our distinctive community offers a natural setting – yet it's perfectly situated to help you take advantage of the Bay Area.", 'Enjoy the possibilities of every day, right here at Park Kiely.', 'Features', '- Full Size Electric Stove Top and Oven', '- Floor to Ceiling Windows', '- Centralized Air Conditioning and Heat*', '- Wall Unit Air Conditioning*', '- Private Patio or Balcony', '- Garbage Disposal', '- Separate Dining Room', 'Community Amenities', '- Immediate Access to the 280 and 880', '- Outdoor Playground', '- Gated Community', '- Pet Friendly', '- Outdoor BBQ Grill', '- Sand Volley Ball Court', '- Pool-Side Cabanas with Gas Grills', '- 2 Swimming Pools', '- Theatre Room', '- Picnic Areas', '- Basketball', '- Courtesy patrol', '- Fitness Center with TV Monitors and Free Weights', '- Dog Park', '- 2 Soothing Spas', '- Buses to Light Rail', 'Pet Policy', 'Please contact us for more details', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'dfbyunGn1z1k']
